<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span style="color:#008000">(١١١٩ - ١١٨٢ هـ)</span> <span style="color:#008000">(١٧٠٧ - ١٧٦٨ م)</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>اسماعيل بن عبد الله الاسكداري،<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>